    "description": "<br><br><br><strong>《海岛物语：序章》</strong>是一款基于回合制的城市建造和战略游戏。在这里你可以建设美丽的城镇、扩展海岛、与外国文明进行贸易或发动战争。探索岛屿的同时，也将会面临困难的问题，需要仔细考虑下一步的行动，因为每一步的选择都可能导致最终的成功或失败！ <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182110/extras/1cb2a6969535768b7db6a91e09346e55.poster.avif?t=1684504451\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182110/extras/1cb2a6969535768b7db6a91e09346e55.webm?t=1684504451\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182110/extras/1cb2a6969535768b7db6a91e09346e55.mp4?t=1684504451\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182110/extras/c74b2093bd0c66ccc3e9f2ca0346dc41.avif?t=1684504451\" width=520 height=109 /></span><br><strong>序章包含：</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 城市建造的全新玩法<br></li><li> 7个介绍游戏基本玩法的关卡</li></ul><br><strong>此外，完整版游戏包含：</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 3场具有挑战任务和不同难度的战役<br></li><li> 超过50种分布在众多生产链上的建筑<br></li><li> 超过30种不同的资源可供提取、加工和生产<br></li><li> 带来别样游戏体验的机制如瘟疫、火灾和寒冬<br></li><li> 战争与贸易<br></li><li> 随机关卡带来的无限乐趣</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182110/extras/328c9d5da0c3aefcc4185ef5fe1e7245.poster.avif?t=1684504451\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182110/extras/328c9d5da0c3aefcc4185ef5fe1e7245.webm?t=1684504451\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182110/extras/328c9d5da0c3aefcc4185ef5fe1e7245.mp4?t=1684504451\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182110/extras/1396ddf42b6c2a385594286bfba049b9.avif?t=1684504451\" width=520 height=109 /></span> <br>一路遇见其他文明、欣赏古老的神庙、与分散在各地的哨站交易，并保护自己不受维京人的掠夺！值得注意的是，肆虐的野蛮人们并不是你唯一的敌人，<strong>火灾</strong>和<strong>瘟疫</strong>同样十分危险。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182110/extras/1c1d7e04e0d69d0824a9934a078e3b85.poster.avif?t=1684504451\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182110/extras/1c1d7e04e0d69d0824a9934a078e3b85.webm?t=1684504451\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182110/extras/1c1d7e04e0d69d0824a9934a078e3b85.mp4?t=1684504451\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
